      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.1309</ph> 	Contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1272e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1272e15" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                The contracting officer shall insert the clause <xref href="52.219-3.dita#FAR_52_219_3"
                              base="i1057314"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.219-3</xref>, Notice of HUBZone Set-Aside or Sole Source Award, in solicitations and contracts for acquisitions that are set aside or awarded on a sole source basis to, HUBZone small business concerns under <xref href="19.1305.dita#FAR_19_1305"
                              base="i1099604"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.1305</xref> or <xref href="19.1306.dita#FAR_19_1306"
                              base="i1099639"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.1306</xref>. This includes multiple-award contracts when orders may be set aside for HUBZone small business concerns as described in <xref href="8.405-5.dita#FAR_8_405_5"
                              base="i1117805"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">8.405-5</xref> and <xref href="16.505.dita#FAR_16_505"
                              base="i1104008"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.505</xref>(b)(2)(i)(F) or when orders may be issued directly to one HUBZone small business concern in accordance with <xref href="19.504.dita#FAR_19_504"
                              base="id203CEK0I0HS"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.504</xref>(c)(1)(ii).</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1272e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                The contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I to waive the 50 percent requirement if the conditions at <xref href="19.1308.dita#FAR_19_1308"
                              base="i1099682"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.1308</xref>(c) apply.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1272e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1272e52" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.219-4.dita#FAR_52_219_4"
                              base="i1057352"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.219-4</xref>, Notice of Price Evaluation Preference for HUBZone Small Business Concerns, in solicitations and contracts for acquisitions conducted using full and open competition.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1272e60" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                The contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I to waive the 50 percent requirement if the conditions at <xref href="19.1308.dita#FAR_19_1308"
                              base="i1099682"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.1308</xref>(c) apply.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1272e68" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            For use of clause <xref href="52.219-33.dita#FAR_52_219_33"
                        base="id203KG0I04WS"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-33</xref>, Nonmanufacturer Rule, see the prescription at <xref href="19.507.dita#FAR_19_507"
                        base="i1100931"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(h)(2).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
